Here is the Spellbook it has only TWO files<br />
1) - EQUI_SpellBookWnd.xml<br />
2) - psb2.tga [512 x 512 image] (Instead of 4 spellbook.tga files)<br />
<a href="http://jimmysheryl.com/Goodies/Pure_SpellBookMod.zip" target="_blank">Pure Spellbook Mod</a> <br />
<br />
The Done button is click on Blue Gem - Pages are brown edges - and placed spells vertical along with names and changed font to Blue - Also the Mem and Scribe bars are hidden at bottom you will see when used <img src="images/smilies/wink.gif" border="0" alt="" title="wink" class="inlineimg" />  Nice size also<br />
<br />
-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-<br />
If you want the bluish tint background along w/ all the fixin's like:<br />
1) - Bluish Tint background and slot background works great when fade at 50 or so.<br />
2) - Modified versions of Player - Group - Target<br />
3) - Small Buff Icon window - Horizontal SpellGems - Hot w/ Inv <br />
4) - Sword cursor w/ Skull Icon in place of boring square box on Spellbook <img src="images/smilies/smile.gif" border="0" alt="" title="smile" class="inlineimg" /><br />
